comments: Ingles (UTA) and George (LAC) briefly engage and separate off-ball.
Beverley (LAC) sets the screen on O'Neale (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Batum (LAC) makes contact with Gobert's (UTA) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Ibaka (LAC) sets the screen in Ingles's (UTA) path and does not deliver contact.
Leonard (LAC) extends his leg into Conley's (UTA) path and trips him during the drive.
George (LAC) places an arm against Ingles (UTA), but does not extend it and Ingles's momentum is what carries him in the same direction.
Batum (LAC) and Gobert (UTA) briefly engage and separate after the pick.
Batum (LAC) makes contact with Conley's (UTA) body that causes him to trip.
George (LAC) sets the screen in Gobert's (UTA) path and absorbs the contact.
Gobert (UTA) makes incidental "high-five" contact with George (LAC) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
